                    "value": "THE PAW PATROL KIDS METAL WATER BOTTLE COMES WITH UNIQUE DESIGN YOU WILL LOVE - Drink in style with Paw Patrol kids insulated water bottle for school. Featuring cool graphics of Chase, Marshall and Skye, the thermos for kids is convenient for your little ones to stay hydrated at school or while traveling. Push button spout allows for easy opening and closing without making a mess. Perfect Paw Patrol kids bottle to carry and on-the-go.",
