                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "THE KIDS STAINLESS STEEL WATER BOTTLE IS FOR KIDS WHO LOVE PAW PATROL - Kids will love to stay hydrated outdoors having the Paw Patrol kids stainless steel water bottle to drink from anytime they're thirsty. Whether at home or traveling in the car, the spout is accessible and easy-to-open thanks to its convenient button. Boys and girls who love Paw Patrol's rescue dogs will love to drink from this colorful kids thermal water bottle.",
